high_descs: Turn right and go to the table.
Pick up the credit card in front of the chair.
Turn right and go across the room to the couch.
Put the credit card on the far right cushion of the couch.
Go back to the table.
Pick up the credit card on the table.
Go back to the couch.
Put the credit card on the far right cushion of the couch to the right of the other credit card.
anns.task_desc: Put two credit cards on the right cushion of the couch.

high_descs: Turn right to face the kitchen table.
Pick up the card on the left of the kitchen table.
Turn right and cross the room and turn right to face the couch.
Place the card on the couch.
Turn right and cross the room and turn right to face the kitchen table.
Pick up the card on the kitchen table.
Turn right and cross the room and turn right to face the couch.
Place the card on the couch.
anns.task_desc: To move two cards from the kitchen table to the couch.

high_descs: Step forward, turn right at the wall to come to a table with two credit cards.
Pick up the credit card closer to the chair.
Turn around, step forward, turn left and walk to the right cushion of the double seated couch.
Place the credit card on the couch.
Turn right, walk forward, turn right, walk to the window, turn left, walk to the table., then turn left to face the table.
Pick up the credit card next to the box.
Return to the double seated couch.
Place the credit card on the couch to the right of the other credit card.
anns.task_desc: Pick up two credit cards and place on the couch.
